summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from Martha Fuson to the south 40 feet of Lot 7, Block 13, Lake Union Addition to the City of Seattle, and Ida Beavers and Averill Beavers, her husband and King County Land Co. to a portion of Lot 12, Block 7, lying Westerly of the right of way of the Oregon & Washington R. R. & Navigation Co. in King County Addition to the City of Seattle.
